data.title: Alexandra Wentworth
data.meta_description: Alexandra Wentworth. Actress: Wenn Liebe so einfach wäre. Alexandra Wentworth was born on 12 January 1965 in Washington, District of Columbia, USA. She is an actress and writer, known for Wenn Liebe so einfach wäre (2009), Jerry Maguire: Spiel des Lebens (1996) and Alles Routine (1999). She has been married to George Stephanopoulos since 20 November 2001. They have two children.
data.text: Alexandra Wentworth was born on January 12, 1965 in Washington, District of Columbia, USA. She is an actress and writer, known for Wenn Liebe so einfach wäre (2009), Jerry Maguire: Spiel des Lebens (1996) and Alles Routine (1999). She has been married to George Stephanopoulos since November 20, 2001. They have two children.
